{"tid":1491892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗事件，今日一週月了，仲記唔記得當日有幾恐佈？","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T01:01:57.000Z","uid":49774,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c2808f34db0010588c995542c692614d508b82","tid":1491892,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16CiwPChpr0&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=09a8a1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0</a><br />\n<br />\n而家既連登好陌生 <br />\n我重睇完一次當日既片 再望一望身邊既人 網上媒體<br />\n大家好似活係平行時空一樣<br />\n大家好似得個知字 但已經忘記左個痛字<br />\n<br />\n想問一句姐 係唔係拉左檢控埋就算？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血債仲洗唔洗還？</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a508af79bc7f328b38c5652064f7fd5fd1ecc2f","tid":1491892,"uid":49774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38Or9bB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38Or9bB.jpg&h=b601ed06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fe22612e409fee26ebbfcbff3970ac270969e07","tid":1491892,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtbJrYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtbJrYc.jpg&h=3eda398c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34c0c8f4b833894c0cb877fe72d1a4a897133db7","tid":1491892,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96750e97946a81f5405e7fbfa6599f3b1ed99a83","tid":1491892,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"永世都記得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823約定你一齊拖手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7時集合 8時築人鏈 9時解散</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">824觀塘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">825荃葵青</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rW37Vhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrW37Vhf.jpg&h=0d9534fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzmtEJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzmtEJW.jpg&h=e1086e13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMiLGXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMiLGXg.jpg&h=6a917a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81TjMph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81TjMph.jpg&h=023181f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84a03cf5032f0ca50bf62b42826fcf6fd4da2a1b","tid":1491892,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9dd9c3429727f6f3d7dfdbb4e7fa088476f774dc","tid":1491892,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3472df515d7ab1c56d962fc5c67b78b55186df6b","tid":1491892,"uid":92967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"由6月到宜家 無一個香港人會忘記所有發過既夢！"},{"pid":"507dd1a650711038e4f5c1d8f0fe2